Thomas Fanning, chief executive 
officer of  Southern Co. (SO) , talks with Bloomberg's Julie Johnsson 
about the company's sales in the southeastern U.S., economic 
growth and the outlook for the expansion of its nuclear energy 
program.  Art Beattie, chief financial officer at Southern, also 
speaks. (Source: Bloomberg)  00:00 Southern's Fanning, Beattie on outlook  Running time 10:16
 